   * MusicBrainz TXXX, artist/album/albumartist support. (#0.539)
   * Added albumartist, originalartist, originalalbum, originaldate,
     recordingdate. (#0.495, #0.546)
   * Ratings, playcount Ogg Vorbis format changed. (#0.544)
   * COMM tags in Ex Falso are deleted properly. (#0.573)
 * UI Changes:
   * Drops from e.g. Nautilus add to playlists/queue. (#0.496)
   * Clear button in Album List. (#0.509)
   * Horizontal scrollbar when absolutely necessary for the song list. (#0.542)
   * "Random" options use filtered lists. (#0.550)
   * Album sort is once again and forever default. (#0.552)
   * 'Add to Playlist' resorts playlist properly. (#0.568)
   * Enter in 'Add a Tag' moves from tag to value. (Debian bug #0.343974)
   * Standard context menu for all browsers.
   * 'Delete' key works in Edit Tags.
   * Type-ahead search works in the Album List.
 * Bug fixes:
   * Double-appearances in the filesystem view. (#0.545)
   * FIFO misses some commands. (#0.548)
   * Stupid 'refresh' signal finally gone. (#0.563)
   * Error when seeking and keyboard can't be grabbed. (#0.572)
